Alternatively, you may request the same FFmpeg source code
from the author for a period of three years from the date of this distribution.

-----------------------------------------------
 3. License Compatibility Note
-----------------------------------------------
Because FFmpeg was statically linked into this DLL:

- If FFmpeg was built with LGPL components:
      The VideoPlayer API Library may be distributed under LGPL or GPL.
      Source code is provided so relinking is possible.

- If FFmpeg was built with GPL components:
      The entire VideoPlayer API Library is covered by GPL and must be GPL.

